last_episode_to_air.name: The Spectacular Finale
last_episode_to_air.overview: Two families face off a final rematch; one draws inspiration from "Beauty and the Beast," while the other draws inspiration from "Aladdin."

name: Be our Chef
overview: Families from diverse backgrounds join a Disney-inspired cooking content at Walt Disney World. In each episode, two familie participate in a themed challenge mixing Disney into their family traditions. The finalists will apply what they have learned to create a dish that represents their family in a Disney way.
